name: nonada-II
description: Picture from Nonada, a hypermedia platform by Mariana Destro (@mariana9destro), 2021, jpg, 640 × 854 px. Nonada is an internet art project composed of five videos, four texts, a virtual installation, and dozens of images. Result of approximately five months of digital file production in 2019–2021, Nonada is a website that emulates the artist's desktop. The digital pieces are accessed by clicks according to the will of whoever is exploring the work.
